OL,3,CYoung man jailed for life for
OL,4,C'execution' shooting of Jesse Lloyd-
OL,5,CSmith
OL,7,FA young man has been jailed for life
OL,8,Ffor the "execution" of a 20-year-old
OL,9,Fman near a community centre dedicated
OL,10,Fto the memory of 10-year-old knife
OL,11,Fcrime victim Damilola Taylor.
OL,13,FJesse Lloyd-Smith was fatally shot in
OL,14,Fthe head in an alleyway close to the
OL,15,FDamilola Taylor Centre in Peckham, and
OL,16,Ffound by his mother just yards from
OL,17,Ftheir home on July 10 2024.
OL,19,FAfter the shooting, Gabriel Charles,
OL,20,F20, fled the country and a Ford S-Max
OL,21,Fcar he had used was burnt out.
