OL,5,CSmith
OL,7,FOn Friday, Charles, from Southwark,
OL,8,Fwas jailed for life with a minimum
OL,9,Fterm of 28 years after being found
OL,10,Fguilty of murder.
OL,12,FSentencing him at the Old Bailey,
OL,13,FJudge Patrick Field KC said: "Jesse's
OL,14,Fkilling was not a spontaneous act. It
OL,15,Fwas an execution, a planned and
OL,16,Fpremeditated murder.
OL,26,@uD@^OU
