OL,3,CYoung man jailed for life for
OL,4,C'execution' shooting of Jesse Lloyd-
OL,5,CSmith
OL,7,F"That planning involved obtaining a
OL,8,Fstolen vehicle, false number plates to
OL,9,Fdisguise its identity, obtaining a
OL,10,Ffirearm and ammunition and carrying
OL,11,Fout surveillance to identify Jesse's
OL,12,Fwhereabouts. I am satisfied you,
OL,13,FGabriel Charles, carried out this
OL,14,Fsurveillance."
OL,16,FThe judge said he could not be sure if
OL,17,FCharles was the gunman or a getaway
OL,18,Fdriver but said it "may not matter" as
OL,19,Fboth intended to kill Mr Lloyd-Smith.
