OL,7,FThe consequences of the murder had
OL,8,Fbeen "profound" and Judge Field paid
OL,9,Ftribute to the remarkable "fortitude
OL,10,Fand quiet dignity" displayed by the
OL,11,Fvictim's family in court.
OL,13,FHe added: "This was in marked contrast
OL,14,Fto the quite frankly appalling
OL,15,Fbehaviour witnessed in the dock during
OL,16,Fthe trial which was nothing short of
OL,17,Fignorant, unfeeling and disrespectful.
OL,18,FThat Jesse's family had to be
OL,19,Fsubjected to this behaviour is
OL,20,Fshameful."
