OL,7,FFive other defendants were sentenced
OL,8,Ffor conspiracy to pervert the course
OL,9,Fof justice.
OL,11,FKywan JN Pierre, 19, from Selhurst,
OL,12,Fsouth London, was locked up for three
OL,13,Fyears; and Ben Nguyen, 20, of no fixed
OL,14,Faddress, was detained for five years
OL,15,Fhaving also been convicted of
OL,16,Fassisting an offender.
OL,18,FA 17-year-old youth, who cannot be
OL,19,Fidentified, and Abdoul Guene, 19, from
OL,20,FPeckham, were both detained for two
OL,21,Fyears.
