OL,7,FEnver Francis, 22, from Southwark, was
OL,8,Fjailed for four years having "taken
OL,9,Fcharge" of the plot to pervert the
OL,10,Fcourse of justice.
OL,12,FThere were shouts of anger from the
OL,13,Fpublic gallery as the five young men
OL,14,Fwere sent down.
OL,16,FPreviously, the court had heard how
OL,17,Fthe silver-coloured Ford S-Max had
OL,18,Fdriven slowly towards the alleyway at
OL,19,Faround 4.50pm last July 10.
