OL,7,FProsecutor James Dawes KC had said:
OL,8,F"The S-Max passed the Damilola Taylor
OL,9,FCentre, turned the corner and stopped."
OL,11,FThe gunman got out of the S-Max and
OL,12,Fran towards the victim, firing at
OL,13,Fleast five shots as he went, jurors
OL,14,Fhad heard.
OL,16,FMr Dawes had said: "Some of the shots
OL,17,Fhit Jesse, knocking him to the ground.
OL,18,FThe gunman ran back to the car which
OL,19,Fdrove away."
