OL,7,FThe victim's mother, Ty Lloyd-Smith,
OL,8,Fwas in her flat only yards away and
OL,9,Fheard the noise of shots.
OL,11,FMr Dawes said: "She saw the shooter
OL,12,Fbut what she could not see was her son
OL,13,Fbecause he was in the alleyway.
OL,15,F"She feared the worst and she shouted
OL,16,Fout Jesse's name."
OL,18,FShe ran downstairs to find her son
OL,19,Flying on the ground, shot in the head,
OL,20,Fjurors heard.
