OL,7,FHis friend, Jamie Burgess, was
OL,8,Ffrantically trying to help him and
OL,9,Ftold police a person called "S" was
OL,10,Finvolved.
OL,12,FThe victim was taken to hospital for
OL,13,Femergency surgery but he died the next
OL,14,Fday.
OL,16,FA search of the scene, with dogs, led
OL,17,Fto the recovery of four spent
OL,18,Fcartridges and two unfired bullets all
OL,19,Ffrom a 9mm automatic pistol.
