OL,7,FThe shooting was partly captured on
OL,8,FCCTV footage although it was from some
OL,9,Fdistance away.
OL,11,FA sixth defendant, Kadjo Kadio, 21,
OL,12,Ffrom Dartford, who voluntarily
OL,13,Fabsented himself from the trial, will
OL,14,Fbe sentenced at a later date for
OL,15,Fassisting an offender and conspiracy
OL,16,Fto pervert the course of justice.
OL,18,FDamilola Taylor, 10, was fatally
OL,19,Fstabbed in Peckham on November 27 2000.
